title: Jieming You
text:
Latest projects


Sähkö Nyt
Electricity price monitoring app for iOS developed entirely with Swift and SwiftUI. Launching early 2023.


Sanajahti Solver
Depth-first search algorithm implementation using Python for solving Sanajahti-game. Web-app built using Flask.


Global Warming analysis
Bayesian Statistics project analysing the global warming trend. HMC (MCMC) simulation written in R and Stan.


Kernel Convolution study
Using simple kernel convolutions to apply e.g., Gaussian Blur on images. Implemented using base R.
